Libre Source Clause

Subject to the terms and conditions of this license, all redistributions, modified
and unmodified, must include the source code encompassing the software itself and 
all 3rd-party non-system application(s) dynamically/statically linked with the software,
as well as the tools required to build the binary form of the software, in its entirety
and full functionality.

Limited Libre Source Clause

Subject to the terms and conditions of this license, all redistributions within 6 months
of availability of the software it was derived from, modified and unmodified, must include
the source code encompassing the software itself and all 3rd-party non-system application(s)
dynamically/statically linked with the software, as well as the tools required to build the
binary form of the software, in its entirety and full functionality.
